                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3683" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0568</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10431 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">三一重工：撬动业绩增长新支点（微案例）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Sany: prying the new fulcrum of performance growth</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杜刚，张丽佳，李佳，张金花，杨舟</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华东师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">三一重工</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8  页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">三一重工；销售模式；按揭贷款；融资租赁；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Sany;sales model;mortgage loan;financial leasing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">三一重工在世界工程机械制造业里排名前五，并且有着“世界泵王”的美誉。凭借强大的设备制造技术和国家政策的支持，三一重工发展迅猛，业绩斐然。但是从2012至2016的5年时间里，国内经济增速放缓，工程设备市场经历寒冬、整个行业遭遇断崖式下滑。依赖信用销售模式的三一重工意识到想要在未来立足市场，不能仅仅依靠政策的便利和少数优质大客户的青睐，要跨过寒冬逆境，就要面对智猪博弈，要更多重视发展下游中小企业这片广阔而充满未知得市场。只有“大猪”、“小猪”携手并进，才能一起生存壮大。但是如何与“小猪”们合作，在养大他们的同时，不用担心自己吃不饱呢？三一重工徘徊犹豫在两种产品信用销售模式——按揭销售和融资租赁。然而，哪一种方式更有利于自己的市场地位和未来发展，这成为三一重工眼下重中之重的考量。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Sany is definitely a leader in the world&#39;s construction machinery manufacturing industry, and has the reputation of &quot;world pump king&quot;. With strong equipment manufacturing technology and national policy support, Sany has developed rapidly and has achieved remarkable results. But in the 5 years——from 2012 to 2016, with the domestic economic growth slowing down, the engineering equipment market experienced a cold winter and the whole industry suffered a cliff type decline. Relying on the model of credit sales, Sany realizes that in the future, they should not only rely on the convenience of the policy and the favor of a few high quality customers, but to cross the cold winter adversity,they should face the game of boxed pigs, and more attention should be paid to the development of the small or medium-sized enterprises in the lower reaches and develop the unknown market. Only upstream and downstream enterprises going hand in hand can make the both survive and grow together. But how do we cooperate with the &quot;Little Pigs&quot; to raise them without worrying about their lack of food? Sany hesitates in two ways of product marketing -- mortgage sales and financial leasing. However, which way is more conducive to its market position and future development? This has become the most important consideration of Sany.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《营销战略》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“制定营销战略与营销计划”， “市场细分”， “目标市场选择”和“市场定位”</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018-12</td>
                            </tr>
